# Skill: Accessibility Audit

1. Run **axe** (CI or extension) on primary flows.
2. Keyboard-only pass (Tab, Shift+Tab, Enter, Space, Esc).
3. Screen reader smoke (VoiceOver or NVDA) on one critical journey.
4. Color contrast check on new text/background pairs.
5. Verify focus management for dialogs and route transitions.

Document failures with **WCAG criterion** references when possible.
